<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA5">
<l>aṇṭak kulattuk katipati yāki yacurari rākkatarai</l>
<l>yiṇṭak kulattai yeṭuttuk kaḷainta viruṭīkē caṉtaṉakku</l>
<l>toṇṭak kulattiluḷ ḷīrvan taṭitoḻu tāyira nāmamcolli</l>
<l>paṇṭaik kulattait tavirttuppal lāṇṭupal lāyirat tāṇṭeṉmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are in the lineage of devotees of him, Hṛṣīkeśa, who, having become</l>
<l>Lord of the lineage of cow-herds and having raised up the lineage of outcastes,</l>
<l rend="indent">exterminated the asuras and rākṣasas,</l>
<l>come, worship [his] feet, say the thousand names, shun the lineage of old,</l>
<l>[and] say many years, many thousands of years!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
